The new Apple iPhone 17 Pro promises - and delivers - big performance enhancements, the upshot of this being a highly significant improvement in triple-A games that prior iPhones have struggled to handle. Oliver Mackenzie gets to grips with the new phone, benchmarks the A19 Pro SoC and stacks it up against prior iPhone generations in this exhaustive review.
